1. Purpose

Set up refined regions by specifying a set of centres and radii about
them.  The refined regions are then the conjunction of these regions.

GT Modifications:
  * Introduce option to override grid merging logic from computational-cost
    driven merging to overlap-driven merging, based on Maxwell release version.
        -- Tanja Bode, 4/2012
